      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "龙套引韩信同上。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00002",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "点绛唇",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "天澹云孤，怨云愁雾，施威武，镇征夫，取胜如神助。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00003",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "韩信上高台，坐。曹参上。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00004",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "曹参"
      ],
      "text": "曹参打躬。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00005",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "一旁侍立。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00006",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "曹参允。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00007",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "暗列兵机神鬼欺，胸藏奥妙少人知。不施万丈深潭计，怎得骊龙项下珠？",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00008",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "俺，韩信。今在九里山下，摆下一座十面阵式，要擒拿项羽。曹参听令。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00009",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "曹参允。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00010",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "命众将披挂整齐，上帐听令。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00011",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
