      "event_id": "02002005_e00029",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "混江龙",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "第三阵艮为山，深伏隘口，第四阵震为雷，实若玄虚。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00030",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "将官乙、将官丙同下。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00031",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "混江龙",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "第五阵巽为风，烟尘浩荡，第六阵离为火，火耗成墟。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00032",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "将官丁、将官戊同下。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00033",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "混江龙",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "第七阵坤为地，要移花接木，第八阵兑为泽，潜在那踪迹。",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00034",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "将官己、将官庚同下。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00035",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "混江龙",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "第九阵安营下寨，第十阵傲荡凶徒，傲荡凶徒。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00036",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "将官辛、魏豹同下。八将同上，四角列阵，二将引项羽同上，入阵，开打，众人同下。",
      "text_length": 38
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00037",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "油葫芦",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "上接着九天纷纷之数，下镇着九天泉以似荒芜。量你有万夫之勇，难逃俺十面埋伏。天之理，天之数，张良用黄公三略法，俺韩信有吕望六韬书，吕望六韬书。",
      "text_length": 70
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00038",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众将、项羽同上，开打，同下。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00039",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "好一场鏖战也！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00040",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "油葫芦",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "只听得呐喊摇旗齐操鼓，纵征驼，亲去取，今番一战定输赢。为君的开基创业，齐天福，为臣的要安邦定国，上功劳簿。平地上起一座战场高埠处，高埠处，列着帅府。更有那张司徒、萧丞相，和那刘高祖，俺韩信在山顶上运计谋，山顶上运计谋。",
      "text_length": 109
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00041",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众将、项羽同上，开打，同下。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00042",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "天下乐",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "又听得动一派萧韵品奏曲，见霸王，见霸王高也么呼，骂韩信是一恶夫。俺只待立刘邦觑伊行如粪土，山顶上常则是活捉拿，纵征驼，亲去取。不提防，列千枝脚登弩，列千枝脚登弩，",
      "text_length": 81
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00043",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众将同上，同耍刀。马童上，开打，同下。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00044",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "天下乐",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "一个逞着雄图，九里山摆着阵图。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00045",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "俺这里！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00046",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "哪吒令",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "望上射似飞蝗骤雨，望下看，大刀和那巨斧。密匝匝队伍，要擒拿项羽，见樊哙旗在手，便麾在垓心内，点起着百万军卒。",
      "text_length": 54
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00047",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "鹊踏枝",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "汉高祖洪福大，俺韩信思扶助，九里山施展六韬书。大会合，亲摆布，托赖着圣天子百灵扶。张子房在高埠处，悲歌声能散楚。楚歌儿吹散了八千子弟归何处？不提防先有埋伏。",
      "text_length": 78
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00048",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众将、项羽同上，开打，同下。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00049",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "胜葫芦",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "中军帐里梦回初，原来是霸王要登途。那虞姬亲把离情诉，腰下借昆吾，血溅了美人图，血溅了美人图。",
      "text_length": 46
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00050",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众人、项羽同上，开打，同下。",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00051",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "么篇",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "正撞着九江王英布，难逃俺十面埋伏。这的是乌江，不是无船渡，错走阴灵路，耻向东吴，耻向东吴。",
      "text_length": 45
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00052",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众将同上，项羽上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00053",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "项羽"
      ],
      "text": "杀了半天，并无问个名儿。呔！尔叫何名？",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00054",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "魏豹"
      ],
      "text": "魏豹大将军，何须通姓名？闻俺须下马，饶恕你残生！",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00055",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "项羽"
      ],
      "text": "魏豹，孤在彭城救你一十八口家眷，今日为何挡孤的去路？看枪！",
      "text_length": 29
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00056",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "魏豹"
      ],
      "text": "大王，我岂不知“报恩”二字？奈韩元帅在山顶上瞭战。我与大王假战三合，引大王出阵便了。",
      "text_length": 42
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00057",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "项羽"
      ],
      "text": "魏豹！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00058",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "魏豹"
      ],
      "text": "有。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00059",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "项羽"
      ],
      "text": "我的儿！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00060",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "魏豹"
      ],
      "text": "吓！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00061",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "项羽"
      ],
      "text": "孤家枪尖下无眼，要你仔细！",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00062",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "魏豹引项羽同下。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00063",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 63,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众将"
      ],
      "text": "项羽逃生！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00064",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 64,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "何人放走？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00065",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 65,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众将"
      ],
      "text": "魏豹放走。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00066",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 66,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "将魏豹斩首。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00067",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 67,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "众将"
      ],
      "text": "魏豹也逃走！",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00068",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 68,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "韩信"
      ],
      "text": "带马追至乌江！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02002005_e00069",
      "play_id": "02002005",
      "scene_id": "02002005_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 69,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖尾声〗。众人同下。",
      "text_length": 10
    }
  ],
  "roles_inferred": true
}